<exercise><statement><p>
      Find the
      
          y-intercepts
        
      for each of the following equations.
    </p><ul><li><m> y \times -1 + x \times 5 = -6 </m></li><li><m> y \times 6 + x \times -1 = 5 </m></li></ul></statement><answer><ul><li><m> 6 </m></li><li><m> \frac{5}{6} </m></li></ul></answer></exercise>
